<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:10:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人质交易或伊朗袭击：德黑兰在与以色列的紧张对峙中加大赌注</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-or-iranian-attack-tehran-ups-the-ante-in-tense-stand-off-with-israel/00000191-4cd7-d699-af95-4ef7040b0000</link><description>加沙停火协议与伊斯兰共和国对贝鲁特和德黑兰暗杀事件的反应之间的联系使得周四在多哈举行的峰会更加具有决定性。布林肯推迟访问该地区的决定表明了局势的紧张和不稳定</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-or-iranian-attack-tehran-ups-the-ante-in-tense-stand-off-with-israel/00000191-4cd7-d699-af95-4ef7040b0000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院法官审查对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的逮捕令请求，以色列做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-as-icc-judges-review-request-for-arrest-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant/00000191-4bd8-dff3-a5d3-4fd801be0000</link><description>在国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、加兰特和哈马斯官员发出逮捕令之前，法官小组必须审查法院是否对涉及以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的事项拥有管辖权，而官员们不知道这一过程可能需要多长时间</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-as-icc-judges-review-request-for-arrest-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant/00000191-4bd8-dff3-a5d3-4fd801be0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登“预计”如果加沙达成停火协议，伊朗将跳过以色列的袭击；报道：哈马斯不会参加多哈会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-live/biden-expects-iran-wont-attack-israel-if-gaza-deal-reached-nyt-hamas-to-miss-talk/00000191-4eaf-d140-a5ff-7eef4bc30000</link><description>美国批准向以色列出售180亿美元的F15战斗机 ■ 美国称卡塔尔将努力确保哈马斯代表出席交易谈判；伊朗消息人士：只有加沙停火协议才能阻止伊朗报复 ■ 以色列国防军呼吁居民在行动前撤离汗尤尼斯的两个社区 ■ 上加利利议会建议居民留在避难所附近，直至另行通知 ■ 以色列国防军确认两名真主党特工在空袭中丧生在黎巴嫩南部的汽车上</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 02:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-live/biden-expects-iran-wont-attack-israel-if-gaza-deal-reached-nyt-hamas-to-miss-talk/00000191-4eaf-d140-a5ff-7eef4bc30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部门拒绝将女同性恋夫妇在孩子的出生证明上登记为“母亲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-refusing-to-register-lesbian-couples-as-mothers-on-childrens-birth-certificate/00000191-4dba-d94f-adf1-ddfefb620000</link><description>内政部违反最高法院裁决，仍坚持写“父母和父母”</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 22:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-refusing-to-register-lesbian-couples-as-mothers-on-childrens-birth-certificate/00000191-4dba-d94f-adf1-ddfefb620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列城市重新考虑保护沿海悬崖免遭当地反对的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-city-rethinks-plan-to-protect-coastal-cliffs-from-crumbling-amid-local-opposition/00000191-4d11-d140-a5ff-7df354730000</link><description>由于海滩游客和水上运动爱好者的反对，以色列中部城市荷兹利亚正在重新考虑在其海岸修建防波堤的计划，他们表示该计划将影响附近海滩上的沙子堆积</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-city-rethinks-plan-to-protect-coastal-cliffs-from-crumbling-amid-local-opposition/00000191-4d11-d140-a5ff-7df354730000</guid></item><item><title>中国和伊朗正在全面战争边缘地区建立第二条丝绸之路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/china-and-iran-are-establishing-a-second-silk-road-in-a-region-on-the-brink-of-all-out-war/00000191-4c81-d485-a1db-ff85a6130000</link><description>传统上，中国会乐于看到美国陷入另一场中东战争。但考虑到伊朗对中国在该地区的举措的重要性，美国知道这次情况并非如此。以色列有吗？</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:13:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/china-and-iran-are-establishing-a-second-silk-road-in-a-region-on-the-brink-of-all-out-war/00000191-4c81-d485-a1db-ff85a6130000</guid></item><item><title>美国批准向以色列提供具有里程碑意义的价值200亿美元的武器包，其中包括价值180亿美元的F15战斗机销售</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/u-s-oks-landmark-20b-arms-package-to-israel-including-18b-f15-fighter-jets-sale/00000191-4d37-d699-af95-4ff7a4e80000</link><description>在国会最终成功通过拜登政府向以色列提供 140 亿美元紧急军事援助几个月后，这一宣布标志着美国历史上最重大的对以色列军售案之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 19:51:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/u-s-oks-landmark-20b-arms-package-to-israel-including-18b-f15-fighter-jets-sale/00000191-4d37-d699-af95-4ff7a4e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉最高法院，迅速结束内塔尼亚胡的审判符合公众利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/ag-to-top-court-public-interest-to-wrap-up-netanyahus-trial-quickly/00000191-4d11-dff3-a5d3-4f196ecd0000</link><description>司法部长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉驳回了因战争而重新审查内塔尼亚胡利益冲突协议的请愿，但强调以色列总理必须避免做出涉及无关因素的决定，特别是涉及与战争有关的决定时</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 19:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/ag-to-top-court-public-interest-to-wrap-up-netanyahus-trial-quickly/00000191-4d11-dff3-a5d3-4f196ecd0000</guid></item><item><title>“惊人的心理准备”：以色列运动员如何在巴黎奥运会上创造历史</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-13/ty-article-podcast/amazing-mental-preparation-how-israeli-athletes-made-history-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-4c53-dae4-afd5-fff7dacd0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 17:18:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-13/ty-article-podcast/amazing-mental-preparation-how-israeli-athletes-made-history-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-4c53-dae4-afd5-fff7dacd0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》调查：以色列军队利用巴勒斯坦平民检查加沙可能埋有诱杀装置的隧道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-uses-gazan-civilians-as-human-shields-to-inspect-potentially-booby-trapped-tunnels/00000191-4c84-d7fd-a7f5-7db6b99e0000</link><description>“我们的生命比他们的生命更重要”：几位消息人士称，没有涉嫌恐怖主义的加沙人被拘留，并在以色列国防军士兵进入之前被派往隧道和房屋中搜查隧道和房屋，以色列高级军官对此一无所知；以色列国防军声称这种做法是被禁止的</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 17:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-uses-gazan-civilians-as-human-shields-to-inspect-potentially-booby-trapped-tunnels/00000191-4c84-d7fd-a7f5-7db6b99e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 312 天：据报道以色列在停战谈判中表现出较小的灵活性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-312-israel-reportedly-showing-less-flexibility-in-truce-talks/00000191-4c69-d9b5-adbf-5c6f808a0000</link><description>伊朗高级官员告诉路透社，只有加沙停火协议才能阻止伊朗直接攻击以色列 ■ 惠誉信用评级机构降低以色列评级，理由是担心加沙战争可能持续到 2025 年 ■ 据报道，伊朗担心以色列、美国可能会采取行动瞄准其核计划以应对袭击 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，以色列在最近的停火谈判中表现出较小的灵活性 ■ 战争已过去 312 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-312-israel-reportedly-showing-less-flexibility-in-truce-talks/00000191-4c69-d9b5-adbf-5c6f808a0000</guid></item><item><title>外交部长表示，在伊朗威胁下，塞浦路斯已做好从以色列和黎巴嫩撤离的准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-13/ty-article/cyprus-ready-for-evacuees-from-israel-and-lebanon-foreign-minister-says-amid-iran-threat/00000191-4c0b-d695-a7b5-de0b3b720000</link><description>由于担心伊朗和真主党可能很快对以色列发动重大袭击，塞浦路斯表示，其从黎巴嫩和以色列撤离外国人的准备工作已经完成</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-13/ty-article/cyprus-ready-for-evacuees-from-israel-and-lebanon-foreign-minister-says-amid-iran-threat/00000191-4c0b-d695-a7b5-de0b3b720000</guid></item><item><title>随着捐款和投票人数的减少，以色列的反政府抗议正处于关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-dwindling-donations-and-turnout-israels-anti-govt-protest-is-at-critical-juncture/00000191-4b70-dbc5-a1fd-eff36d060000</link><description>加沙战争爆发八周后，以色列民主总部组织恢复了以色列的抗议运动，但10月7日过去了10个月，该组织尚未实现其主要目标</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-dwindling-donations-and-turnout-israels-anti-govt-protest-is-at-critical-juncture/00000191-4b70-dbc5-a1fd-eff36d060000</guid></item><item><title>五名涉嫌在斯德泰曼虐待哈马斯囚犯的以色列士兵将被软禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-hamas-prisoner-to-be-sent-to-house-arrest/00000191-4bde-d7fd-a7f5-7bfe884c0000</link><description>由于完成缓刑审查所需时间较长，且考虑到嫌疑人有家人且释放后不会对公众构成威胁，以色列军方检方同意将嫌疑人软禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:08:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-hamas-prisoner-to-be-sent-to-house-arrest/00000191-4bde-d7fd-a7f5-7bfe884c0000</guid></item><item><title>即使加沙停火达成，报复的欲望可能会危及以色列与真主党的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/zero-hour-gaza-summit-is-no-longer-about-hostages-but-on-aborting-all-out-regional-war/00000191-4b24-dfee-a3f3-5fe641d50000</link><description>以色列、真主党和伊朗之间的反应等式使得加沙停火作为防止全面地区战争的工具具有重要的战略意义，但它却将人质释放推向了边缘。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 11:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/zero-hour-gaza-summit-is-no-longer-about-hostages-but-on-aborting-all-out-regional-war/00000191-4b24-dfee-a3f3-5fe641d50000</guid></item><item><title>排水沟中发现的碎石记录了古代耶路撒冷被毁前的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-13/ty-article/detritus-found-in-drainage-channel-captures-ancient-jerusalem-life-before-its-destruction/00000191-4b4c-d695-a7b5-df4da3140000</link><description>以色列文物管理局表示，陶器发现物和一个完整的玻璃瓶是罗马时期古代耶路撒冷餐具的典范，尽管其主人可能并没有长期享用它们</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 11:10:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-13/ty-article/detritus-found-in-drainage-channel-captures-ancient-jerusalem-life-before-its-destruction/00000191-4b4c-d695-a7b5-df4da3140000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔在圣殿山参观期间：我们的目标是允许犹太人祈祷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-during-inflammatory-temple-mount-visit-our-goal-is-to-permit-jewish-prayer/00000191-4b09-d026-afb7-7bafc7cf0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，极右翼部长对圣地的访问违反了那里的现状，而现状仍然没有改变。 “圣殿山没有个人政策——无论是国家安全部长的政策还是其他任何人的政策”</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 09:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-during-inflammatory-temple-mount-visit-our-goal-is-to-permit-jewish-prayer/00000191-4b09-d026-afb7-7bafc7cf0000</guid></item><item><title>惠誉下调以色列信用评级，称“加沙战争可能持续到2025年”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/fitch-lowers-israels-credit-rating-says-gaza-war-could-last-well-into-2025/00000191-4a3f-d633-a393-cfbf0daa0000</link><description>惠誉是自加沙战争爆发以来三大评级机构中最后一家下调以色列信用评级的机构，此前穆迪和标准普尔财政部长斯莫特里奇表示，此举是“预期的”，理由是以色列迄今为止“代价最为高昂的生存战争”</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 05:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/fitch-lowers-israels-credit-rating-says-gaza-war-could-last-well-into-2025/00000191-4a3f-d633-a393-cfbf0daa0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和加兰特为以色列打地区战争做好准备，双方的战线升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/gallant-cant-hide-his-disdain-for-israels-netanyahu-who-cant-help-fanning-the-flames/00000191-4826-d27c-a5fb-efffc6ac0000</link><description>加兰特知道自己不会被解雇，因此他对他的老板、以色列总理进行了恶毒的讽刺，称有关加沙“全面胜利”的言论是“无稽之谈”。人们可能预计内塔尼亚胡会表现出克制，要么无视加兰特的言论，要么发表更理智的声明</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article/.premium/gallant-cant-hide-his-disdain-for-israels-netanyahu-who-cant-help-fanning-the-flames/00000191-4826-d27c-a5fb-efffc6ac0000</guid></item><item><title>怀着沉重的心情和对国家零信心，退伍的基布兹尼克人返回加沙边境的家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-heavy-hearts-and-no-faith-in-the-state-kibbutzniks-return-to-their-gaza-border-homes/00000191-4835-d667-a9d7-cdb58d4f0000</link><description>梅法西姆居民被疏散到荷兹利亚的一家酒店，在那里重建了他们的基布兹，十个月后，他们现在开始搬回家——尽管战争在距离这里不到一英里的地方肆虐。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-heavy-hearts-and-no-faith-in-the-state-kibbutzniks-return-to-their-gaza-border-homes/00000191-4835-d667-a9d7-cdb58d4f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>